node.text: My name is Reuben Khalife, and I will discover what I don’t know. After AIT for the National Guard, I will look online and get training at AIT...look online at what I do for AIT and what they train me on. I will measure my success by being better every week that I am at AIT and by recording what I get: every physical test, and what the sergeants, like, say about me. The learning I will have to be is...I will have to have hands-on because I am energetic person, so I like to do stuff that makes me work for it. In life, you have to have money skills so that you can pay for rent and other stuff like cars and your electricity bill. You have to have good talking skills so you will be able to get a job and find work. I’m going to be an aviation operations specialist because, in the army, they make good money and I can get jobs from being that at air force. Thank you.

node.text:
When you are at home with the rain battering down the window pane it is the universal drool to think of bhajjias and chai. So while I sat in my balcony enjoying the rain and eating hot bhajjias I happened to look across the street and saw this little child in his shanty with a vada pav. He was cold and shivering and that pav was maybe the only food he would get.  And then it struck me what to some is just pleasure or indulgence for another it is sustenance. How often we forget to appreciate what we have.  Even the little things that give us pleasure.  How often we run behind what we don’t have never for a moment stopping to see truly what we already have achieved or possess. Let me take a moment to do that today.

node.text:
Semusa emitiu novo informe com a situação epidemiológica da cidade

Informe epidemiológico da Secretaria Municipal de Saúde (Semusa) confirmou três óbitos por Covid-19 em Anápolis, neste sábado (22).

As vítimas, de acordo com a pasta, são um homem de 88 anos, que faleceu no dia 20 de agosto; uma mulher de 77 anos, que foi a óbito no dia 21; e uma mulher, 31 anos, que morreu hoje.

Esta última, foi a professora da rede municipal Camilla Graciano. A partida repentina comoveu a cidade, que já tem 171 vitimas fatais da Covid-19.

No informe, a Semusa também trouxe o acréscimo de mais 81 casos da doença nas últimas 24h e agora Anápolis já registra 7.322 confirmações.

A pasta afirma que 5.001 já se recuperaram e diz que os demais pacientes estão internados ou em isolamento domiciliar.
.
.

Kenapa harus Baby De?

Baby De merupakan produk baru dari Techno DE Japan, Moms. Dengan teknologi Human sterilization system dari jepang yang mengandung Hypochlorous Acid (HOCl) 50 ppm(0.005 %).

Baby De Sanitizer aman digunakan bagi bayi dibawah umur 5 tahun dan menjaga bayi Moms tetap sehat, aktif dan terhindar dari berbagai penyakit.

Baby De sudah terbukti aman loh Moms 👌👌👌

node.text:
My son would ask anxiously, “Mommy, why are changing into your going-out clothes? Do you have to go somewhere?” each time I would got ready to go to work. 

As a global trainer and coach, work often took me away from home. One year I traveled to a different city around the world every week, coming home for the weekends - only to spend the time in front of the computer catching up on yet more work.

As a single mother of 2 kids I found it impossible to prioritize family over work. I inherited my #workethic from my immigrant parents - that ‘putting food on the table’ came first at all costs, that making money to support the family is how we #loveandcare for our family. 

All these years I wished work was less busy, that I could slow down to spend more time with the kids and be there for them before they all grew up. In reality, my domestic helper did the work of taking care of the kids and the home while I worked.
It wasn’t until heaven intervened and ‘scheduled’ #COVID-19 and my domestic helper’s early departure to coincide, for our wish to come true. 

Suddenly, I had to adjust work priorities to reduce my workload. I now spent more than half of each day tending to dishes, laundry, shopping and food - for the first time, I literally #putfoodonthetable, with much reduced income to do so.

The kids had to learn how to help with #housework, and be willing to take on these tasks that used to be the helper’s responsibility - a lot of “Why me?” “Why do I have to do this?” And of course, we all had to #self-quarantine and stay at home together for days on end as the #pandemic continued.

In the end, it was the #bestthingever to happen to us.

Through caring for our home we learned how to care for each other - we finally came #TOGETHER as a family. 

As I was leaving home the other day to buy groceries, my son happily said “Bye Mommy!” I suddenly realized it had been a while since he clung to me anxiously when I left home. He no longer worried I was leaving him behind.

node.text:
¿Qué hacer si tenemos un paciente con COVID-19 en casa?
Es importante saber cómo actuar en casa si un familiar es diagnosticado con COVID 19. Por ello, queremos compartir las siguientes recomendaciones para su correcto cuidado y atención:

-Debe usar mascarilla de manera permanente en casa.
-Comida normal y reposo relativo.
-Deberá hidratarse bien (más de 2 litros al día).
-Deberá usar baño propio y toalla de papel
-Sus utensilios deben ser lavados con agua hervida o desinfectarlos.
-Lavar su ropa o toallas con agua caliente más de 50 grados o se usa solución de lejía con 5 partes de agua.
-No entrar en contacto con personas de tercera edad ni gestantes dentro de su casa.
-Sus familiares deberán usar mascarilla cuando tengan que atenderlo o socializar con él de cerca, si es una persona que no se vale por sí mismo, la persona que lo atiende debe usar guantes normales (no requiere guantes quirúrgicos).

Dr. Eduardo Gotuzzo Herencia
Infectólogo

node.text: You will find your way at your own pace and that is absolutely okay 💕

Every flower blooms in its own time

I lately have been comparing myself to my peers 

They are all starting their careers. And I am at home due to my mental health

This has caused me to feel bad about myself. Why are they ready but I’m not? What’s wrong with me? Did I choose the wrong career path? 

I am trying to sift my mindset to the message in this quote

Every flower blooms in its own time

I am not personally ready to bloom into my career yet and that is okay!! My time will come🌼

node.text:
പറപ്പൂരുകാർ ലോകത്തിന് മുന്നിൽ വീണ്ടും മാതൃകയാകുകയാണ്.

കൊവിഡിനെതിരായ പോരാട്ടത്തിൽ  പറപ്പൂരുകാർക്ക് അഭിമാനത്തോടെ പറയാവുന്ന മറ്റൊരു പേരാണ് മലപ്പുറം ജില്ലയിലെ കുഴിപ്പുറം‌ സ്വദേശിയായ ഹസ്കർ അലി ചക്കരത്തൊടി.

ലോകം മുഴുവനും മാനവരാശിയെ ഒന്നടങ്കം ബാധിച്ച കോവിഡ് എന്ന ഈ മഹാമാരിയെ തുരത്തുന്ന പോരാട്ടത്തിൽ മുഴുകിയ സമയമാണിത്. ഫലപ്രദമായ വാക്സിൻ കണ്ടുപിടുത്തം കൊണ്ട് മാത്രമേ നമുക്ക് ഈ രോഗത്തിൽ നിന്നും പൂർണ്ണ ആശ്വാസം ലഭിക്കുകയുള്ളൂ, അതിനുവേണ്ടി  യുഎഇ ആരോഗ്യ വകുപ്പും ചൈനയിലെ സിനോഫാം കമ്പനിയും ചേർന്ന് വാക്സിൻ ഉത്പാദിപ്പിക്കാനുള്ള ശ്രമങ്ങൾ നടത്തിക്കൊണ്ടിരിക്കുകയാണ്, ആ പരിശ്രമങ്ങളുടെ മൂന്നാം ഘട്ടമെന്നോണം #4humanity എന്ന ഹാഷ് ടാഗോടെ അബുദാബിയിലും ഈ അടുത്തായി ഷാർജയിലും അതിന്റെ ട്രയൽ നടക്കുകയാണ്. ദൃഢനിശ്ചയത്തോടെ ചിലരെങ്കിലും മുന്നോട്ടു വന്നാൽ മാത്രമേ ഈ നടന്നു വരുന്ന വാക്സിൻ പരീക്ഷണങ്ങളും വിജയ സോപാനത്തിൽ എത്തിക്കാൻ കഴിയുകയുള്ളൂ എന്നതും ഒരു നഗ്നസത്യമാണ്. ഷാർജയിൽ നടക്കുന്ന ട്രയലിൽ അഭിമാനത്തോടെ പങ്കെടുക്കാൻ കഴിഞ്ഞു എന്ന ചാരിതാർഥ്യം 'എന്റെ സ്വന്തം പറപ്പൂരിനോട് ' പങ്കുവെക്കുകയാണ് ഹസ്‌കർ.  അത് പോലെത്തന്നെ യുഎഇലുള്ള മറ്റുള്ളവർക്ക് ഈ ദൗത്യത്തിൽ പങ്കെടുക്കാൻ ഒരു പ്രചോദനവുകമാകട്ടെ എന്നാശിക്കുകയാണ് അദ്ദേഹം. 

വാക്‌സിൻ ടെസ്റ്റ് സെന്റർ അബൂദാബിയിൽ തുറന്ന അന്ന് മുതൽ ഈ പരീക്ഷണത്തിന്റെ ഭാഗമാകണമെന്നു മനസ്സിൽ ഉറപ്പിച്ചിരുന്നു ഹസ്കർ. യാത്രാ നിയന്ത്രണങ്ങൾ ഉണ്ടായതിനാൽ തന്റെ പങ്കാളിത്തം കുറച്ചു വൈകിപ്പോയി എങ്കിലും, ഷാർജയിലെ സെന്ററിൽ നിന്നും വാക്സിന്റെ ആദ്യ ഡോസ് എടുത്തിട്ട് ഇന്നേക്ക് ഒരാഴ്ചയിൽ അധികം കഴിഞ്ഞിരിക്കുന്നു. ആദ്യ ഡോസ് കഴിഞ് 21 ദിവസം കഴിഞ്ഞാൽ അടുത്ത ഡോസ് എടുക്കണം അതിനിടയിൽ ആരോഗ്യ വകുപ്പിലെ ഉദ്യോഗസ്ഥർ  വിവരങ്ങൾ അന്വേഷിച്ചു ബന്ധപ്പെട്ടുകൊണ്ടിരിക്കുന്നു.

സർവ്വശക്തന്റെ അനുഗ്രഹത്താൽ ആ ചരിത്ര ഉദ്ധ്യമത്തിൽ തനിക്ക് 15 വർഷമായി അന്നം തരുന്ന യുഎഇ എന്ന മഹത്തായ രാഷ്ട്രത്തിന്റെ കോവിഡിനെതിരെയുള്ള പോരാട്ടത്തിൽ പങ്കാളിയായതിൻെറ സന്തോഷം 'എന്റെ സ്വന്തം പറപ്പൂർ' നോട് പങ്ക് വെച്ചു.

കോവിഡ് 19 മഹാമാരിക്കെതിരെയുള്ള വാക്‌സിൻ പരീക്ഷണം ലോകത്ത് പലയിടത്തും നടന്നു കൊണ്ടിരിക്കുന്നു. സാധാരണ ജീവിതത്തിലേക്കു തിരിച്ചു പോവാനുള്ള വലിയ പ്രതീക്ഷയാണ് വാക്‌സിൻ. ആ പ്രതീക്ഷകൾ വിജയകരമാവട്ടെ എന്ന് പ്രത്യാശിക്കാം. 

ഈ മഹാമാരിയിൽ നിന്നുംപൂർണ്ണമായും മുക്തമായി നമുക്ക് പഴയജീവിതത്തിലേക്ക് എത്രയും പെട്ടെന്ന് എത്താനാവട്ടെ എന്ന് നമുക്ക് പ്രാർത്ഥിക്കാം. 

#കോവിഡിനെതിരെ_പറപ്പൂർ_ഒറ്റക്കെട്ട്
#Parappur
#covid

Image may contain: indoor, text that says 'Robot Servers Ready to Overtake a New Hot Pot Restaurant on the Las Vegas Strip X Pot opened its lounge at the Grand Canal Shoppes, but the robots await their turn to serve when the dining room debuts By Susan Stapleton August 20, 2020 3:00 pm'.

node.text:
The robots do not function yet, but the food is ready at X Pot, the new hot pot restaurant now open at the Grand Canal Shoppes at the Palazzo. The restaurant opened its lounge area, with the dining room with robot servers debuting later.
Once completely open, the restaurant promises an entertainment experience with 360-degree projections in high-def, interactive light shows, and themed sounds to accompany the thousand-year-old Sichuan hot-pot tradition.
Founders Haibin Yang and David Zhao of Chubby Cattle fame in Chinatown bring the restaurant with its Asian fusion dishes, complete with A5 Wagyu beef and certified Kobe beef dry-aged for 100 days in a case in the dining room. Customers then can select the quality and level of meat, based on how long the beef has been aged. Diners also choose and cook their own ingredients, ranging from meat and seafood to vegetables, and cook them at communal tables.
For now, the lounge offers a tight menu of oyster shooters, wagyu beef sushi, seafood platters, and marinated cherry tomatoes.
When the dining room opens, X Pot will feature performances that include ancient Chinese face-changing ceremonies, noodle dances, and table animation shows, each paired with its smart-robot technology. (Article by Eater Las Vegas)  #cocktailwaitresses #bottlegirls #lasvegas #pandemic #covid #robot

node.text:
Champiñones al ajillo🤤😍
.
INGREDIENTES:

1 kg de champiñones.
3 dientes de ajo.
Perejil fresco.
Aceite de oliva, pimienta negra recién molida y sal.

Preparación:

Limpiar los champiñones con un paño muy limpio o servilleta
Corta los champiñones en láminas.

Pela los dientes de ajo y córtalos en rodajas.

Pon una sartén a fuego medio con un poco de aceite y cuando esté caliente colocar los ajos y procura que se doren por ambos lados, sin llegar a quemarse.

Cuando estén con un tono dorado agregar los champiñones a la sartén junto con un poco de sal y pimienta negra recién molida, y cocínalos unos 10 minutos a fuego suave, removiéndolos de vez en cuando.

Pon el fuego fuerte y cocínalos 5 minutos más.

Lava, seca y pica las hojas de perejil, cantidad al gusto.

Apaga el fuego, añade el perejil cortado y mézclalo con los champiñones.
.

node.text: @tow_nee_ Have you heard the news about @wearebodypolitic  and @longcovidsos meeting with the @who? It’s really fascinating and great news for us longhaulers.
@my.longcovid.journey just recently started following them in the last hour from a reddit forum, how I found your page

@tow_nee_ oh interesting! Yeah they are doing great work. And they are suffering all the while.😒 Just trying to do my little part over here! Going public is pretty nerve wrecking, but a small price to pay to spread awareness.
With anything in life, you don’t really understand something until you go through it.
@my.longcovid.journey just recently started following them in the last hour from a reddit forum, how I found your page

@tow_nee_ oh interesting! Yeah they are doing great work. And they are suffering all the while.😒 Just trying to do my little part over here! Going public is pretty nerve wrecking, but a small price to pay to spread awareness.

I find it physically painful to see people out and about, not wearing masks, not seeming cautious, and living as if there is no pandemic. This concerns me on many levels.
⁣
I wouldn’t want anyone to have their life yanked out from under them the way mine was. Like so many others, I was fine and healthy. In a blink of an eye, my life changed. I wouldn’t want anybody hurting, physically, mentally, and emotionally, the way I am. I wouldn’t want anyone going through what I’m going through. 
⁣
There’s nothing I can do or say to anybody to really drive it home. Even the fact that I’ve suddenly fallen ill doesn’t get through. Or that I haven’t worked in over a month. Or that I haven’t driven my car in two.
⁣
I spoke to my husband and asked, “Had I not become a longhauler, what would our opinions be?” He was lucky. He beat the virus in 12 days with no lasting symptoms. Had I done the same, would we take it as seriously? 
⁣
I try to put myself in other people’s shoes. Maybe had I beaten the virus fully, I would also loosen up a bit and actually go to the grocery store, see friends (social distancing and masks), and take my son places like outdoor museums and such, instead of being on house arrest. Because it’s true. No one gets it ‘til they get it. What would I need to hear in order to understand without having to be sick?
⁣
I don’t personally know anyone else within my circle of friends or community who is a long hauler. Had I not gotten sick, I wouldn’t have spent the weeks I have spent in the support groups learning more and more about what this virus has done to thousands. Unaffected people don’t spend time in the groups. Most people are basically still unaware long haulers exist. Especially my doctors.
⁣
This is one of the reasons I felt an urge to start this account. The community of long haulers I’m connected with in the groups are well aware, but most of the people in my life are not. This was a way for me to be productive while lying in bed. This was a way to connect with new long haulers who were just as confused as I was after the two week mark. This was a way for me to connect with longer haulers than I.
⁣
It really is up to us to educate people.

node.text:
🤱🤱El bebé y la madre crean una lazo de amor y bienestar atravez de la lactancia materna, no sólo lo alimenta con leche si no que también le brinda seguridad confianza y amor.
🤱Ambos se benefician con la práctica de la lactancia materna.
▫️
👉🏻Para los bebés
La leche materna es la fuente de alimento natural para los bebés menores de 1 año. Esta leche:
▪️
🤍Tiene las cantidades adecuadas de carbohidratos, proteínas y grasa
🤍Proporciona las proteínas digestivas, minerales, vitaminas y hormonas que los bebés necesitan
🤍Tiene anticuerpos que ayudan a evitar que su bebé se enferme.
▫️
👉🏻Para las mamás
▪️
🤍Establecerá un vínculo único entre usted y su bebé
🤍Descubrirá que es más fácil bajar de peso
🤍Demorará el inicio de sus periodos menstruales
🤍Disminuirá el riesgo de enfermedades, como diabetes tipo 2, ciertos tipos de cáncer de ovarios y de mama, osteoporosis, enfermedades del corazón y obesidad
▫️
🏥Centro Médico Buenos Aires

Don't miss this important presentation! Note that this meeting will occur on a Tuesday and include a live (see the Rotary Club of Oakland’s YouTube channel) 50-minute panel discussion.

COVID-19 is a global crisis, but it's not affecting everyone equally. This special event, hosted by the Rotary Club of Oakland, will examine how health, economic, and racial inequities are converging during the pandemic, and how we can create better outcomes for individuals, communities, and our nation.

Panelists:
Dr. Mary C. Daly, President and CEO, Federal Reserve Bank of San Francisco
Dr. Anthony Iton (MD, JD, PHD), Senior Vice President, Healthy Communities, The California Endowment
Dr. Carmen Rojas, President and CEO, Marguerite Casey Foundation, and Founder, The Workers Lab

Moderator:
Dr. Robert Ogilvie, Oakland Director, SPUR (San Francisco Bay Area Planning and Urban Research Association) #covid19 #covid_19 #covid #inequality #federalreservebank #buildinghealthycommunities #magueritecaseyfoundation #sfplanningandurbanresearch

node.text:
Contra o CORONAVÍRUS, a PaLyn oferece a PROTEÇÃO!

Além de combater a PANDEMIA através de nosso serviço de DESINFECÇÃO, nós eliminamos também as micropartículas de bactérias das superfícies que causam desde odores até mesmo uma transmissão de vírus que pode afetar a sua saúde.

Aplicamos uma NEBULIZAÇÃO de produto, ela cria uma película protetora que vai te deixar SEGURO por vários dias, porque mesmo que uma pessoa esteja infectada pelo coronavírus espirre neste local, o próprio vírus é eliminado pelo resíduo do produto.
Assim você guarda a VIDA não só da sua família, mais dos colaboradores, clientes e transeuntes que passam pelo mesmo local que você.

Lugares que tem o fluxo de pessoas muito grande é inevitável fazer a SANITIZAÇÃO periodicamente  nesse estabelecimento, e por isso nós estamos CERTIFICADOS de acordo com as os órgãos fiscalizadores como a ANVISA e Ministério da Saúde.

@felhersu estoy aprendiendo del mejor en su técnica

Como  te dije ayer @mariandrepalacios te  admiro..... 🤗🤗🤗🤗
@vsterlingr mi Vane cuanto hemos avanzado y jamás volveremos donde ya estuvimos
Como el viejo adagio: para.atrás ni.para coger impulsos, la vida sabe donde me.llevará, sin miedo a los cambios 😍😘
Totalmente de acuerdo @mariandrepalacios Jamás volveremos donde ya estuvimos.  Ha sido un desplazamiento para crecer, sin duda, mucho que agradecer a estos meses de distanciamiento social.🤗😙

Nada más cierto que tus palabras en este post ... cuanto hemos aprendido ...extrañado ... y a decir te quiero! son tiempos muy duros y tal vez para ti más ... pues rememoro a cuando mi papá decidió irse a otro plano y es algo que nunca dejará de doler...aunque a veces me ostino de todo esto, confieso que tampoco quiero volver a la normalidad... te abrazo mariandre 😙

Nada más cierto que tus palabras en este post ... cuanto hemos aprendido ...extrañado ... y a decir te quiero! son tiempos muy duros y tal vez para ti más ... pues rememoro a cuando mi papá decidió irse a otro plano y es algo que nunca dejará de doler...aunque a veces me ostino de todo esto, confieso que tampoco quiero volver a la normalidad... te abrazo mariandre 😙

No, no quiero regresar a la "normalidad" porque lo único que extraño de ella es la presencia física de mi mamita que murió en tiempos de #pandemia

En estos casi seis meses de distanciamiento social he aprendido más que en toda una vida lo valiosa que soy, la fuerza interna que tengo para seguir adelante, quizás muchos dirán y a mí qué me importa tu historia, pero es que si te sientas un rato y piensas todo lo que has hecho en estos meses seguro te darás cuenta del poder que descubriste en tu interior, esas ganar de salir adelante aunque todo futuro parece incierto, has aprendido a vivir el ahora, a decir más te quiero a las personas que tienes a tu lado pero sobre todo a ti mismo/a, y te has encontrado con tus demonios internos.

No voy a negar que para todos ha sido duro, muy duro, y seguro seguiremos aprendiendo pero también sé que no importa lo que suceda en las próximas horas o días todos tenemos una versión mejorada.

Y ¿tú estás seguro que quieres regresar a la normalidad?

#miretrato #vida #reflexionnocturna #covid-19

node.text: Diskusi malam minggu dengan "Mick Jegger Ubud" Om Dian Hanandia Nataprawira dan Pak Sim. Bagi teman teman yang belum mengenal Pak Sim, beliau adalah pemilik dari Delta Dewata Supermarket dan Mini Market yang tersebar di seluruh Gianyar, yang menjadikan beliau menjadi salah satu pengusaha lokal yang dikenal di Bali. Tema diskusinya masih seputar industri pariwisata dan pandemi covid 19. Namun yang menjadi kesimpulan diskusi tadi malam adalah alam ternyata sudah memberikan tanda tanda kepada manusia tentang pandemi ini antara lain berupa letusan gunung Agung. Dua tahun yang lalu saya berfikir bagaimana industri pariwisata Bali mampu bertahan di tengah letusan gunung Agung? Ternyata banyak di antara kami yang juga mencoba memahami apa makna dibalik letusan gunung Agung yang senantiasa mengeluarkan letupan letupan sehingga mengakibatkan travel warning dari Australia saat itu. Kami kemudian sepakat bahwa UMKM adalah satu satunya industri yang mampu mempertahankan ekonomi rakyat, tidak hanya di Bali namun diseluruh Indonesia. Semoga kita semua tetap sehat, tabah dan mampu bertahan melewati masa masa sulit ini #latenightdiscussion #deltacoffeeroastery #deltacoffee #tourismindustry #hospitalityindustry #retail #retailindustry #industripariwisata #ekonomikerakyatan #ukm #umkm #umkmindonesia #pandemic #pandemiclife #covid #covid_19 #covid19indonesia #ubudcommunity #ubudlife #islandlife #islandlife🌴 #jakartaninubud #ubud #bali

node.text:
Simaria testa positivo para a covid-19, está assintomática e em isolamento

A cantora Simaria, da dupla com Simone, testou positivo para a covid-19 na tarde de ontem. A informação foi confirmada hoje pelo UOL com a assessoria de imprensa dela.
Simaria está "totalmente assintomática" e sendo acompanhada pelo médico infectologista David Uip, que integra o comitê de contenção do coronavírus no estado de São Paulo.

De acordo com a assessoria, a cantora "está seguindo os devidos protocolos de isolamento" em sua casa em Alphaville, na grande São Paulo.
A família tinha uma viagem programada para a Espanha, onde a cantora tem uma casa. Por exigências do país de destino, todos foram testados. Simaria foi a única que recebeu resultado positivo; seu marido e filhos não estão contaminados, informou a assessoria.
"Me sinto bem, sem nenhum sintoma, porém o mais difícil está sendo ficar isolada dos meus filhos sem poder abraçá-los", disse Simaria, em nota.

Divulgação Barra News - Reportagem UOL

One of the most famous studies of obedience in psychology was carried out by Stanley Milgram, a psychologist at Yale University. He conducted an experiment focusing on the conflict between obedience to authority and personal conscience.

65% (two-thirds) of participants continued to the highest level of 450 volts. All the participants continued to 300 volts.

Conclusion - Ordinary people are likely to follow orders given by an authority figure, even to the extent of killing an innocent human being.  Obedience to authority is ingrained in us all from the way we are brought up.

People tend to obey orders from other people if they recognize their authority as morally right and/or legally based. This response to legitimate authority is learned in a variety of situations, for example in the family, school, and workplace. 

"The extreme willingness of adults to go to almost any lengths on the command of an authority constitutes the chief finding of the study and the fact most urgently demanding explanation." - Stanley Milgram

This right here is something that should be known far and wide. This experiment proves the absolute importance of psychology, both of the Individual and the Crowd, and showcases just how much blind belief in any authority figure is one of the most dangerous belief that exists in our world today. What one needs to understand is that we live in a society that is run by those who do NOT have the best interest of Humanity at heart. They have a very advance Knowledge of Human Psychology and know exactly which buttons to press to make an Individual tick the way they want him/her to tick.

In case you still did not catch the very basic essence of this experiment and the horrors blind belief in authority does... NOT ONE participant categorically REFUSED to Harm another human  because the "authority" asked them to. They ALL went along with it, some more than others.
This blind belief in authority is one half of the equation... the other is the importance of Morality in a person's Life, and why, when it is lacking, people will do anything and justify it.

Série COVID.19 - CARRETEIROS (Marau/RS) "Alguns analistas colocam que a carreta da região colonial italiana, devido a peculiaridades geográficas, era formada por um caixão, quatro rodas, um eixo e um breque, este de fundamental importância devido às íngremes descidas de montanhas e serras.
Segundo analistas, a engenhosidade do italiano e de seus descendentes permitiu a adaptação do veículo as condições topográficas de vida da colônia, o que também exigiu, em contraposição à paciência, mansidão e coragem." (Fonte: Colonos, Carreteiro e comerciantes. João Carlos Tedesco)

node.text:
★【横浜赤レンガ倉庫1号館　シアター赤レンガ】様へウイルス抑制効果のあるコーティング﻿
﻿
《抗ウイルスコーティング》を施工させていただきました♪﻿
﻿
ご依頼いただき誠にありがとうございました！﻿
﻿
﻿
★ 《抗ウイルスコーティング》は﻿
﻿
インフルエンザウイルスなどの﻿
【エンベロープ型ウイルス】を減少させる効果があり、﻿
北里大学研究センターの試験結果によると、﻿
﻿
インフルエンザなどの﻿
【エンベロープ型ウイルス】を﻿
《1時間で91%、8時間で98%減少》させるという結果がでております。﻿
﻿
また、空気中の水分と反応し効果を発揮する﻿
《空気触媒》の為、光のない環境や屋内での効果も期待できます。﻿
﻿
接触感染を防ぐ対策としては申し分のない性能がございます。﻿
﻿
株式会社ジェブではこれからも、人々の満足と、地球環境の保護を目指してまいります。﻿
﻿
シアター赤レンガ様、﻿
﻿
この度は誠にありがとうございました。﻿
﻿
今後も益々のご発展をお祈り申し上げます。﻿
﻿
﻿

node.text:
Uber saldrá de California por regulaciones del Estado!

California ( USA ), 22 de agosto (MCI) – A Uber se suma también Lyft, quienes tendrán que cerrar completamente las operaciones en California. Arruinan empresas y el empleo de miles de personas. Este viernes, Uber y Lyft cerraron completamente las operaciones de transporte compartido en California.

En septiembre de 2019, la legislatura del estado de California aprobó la AB 5, una ahora famosa ley que restringe severamente la contratación independiente y el trabajo por cuenta propia en muchas industrias. Al requerir que las aplicaciones de uso compartido como Uber y Lyft reclasifiquen a sus conductores como empleados de pleno derecho, la ley ordenó que las compañías provean asistencia médica y beneficios a todos los conductores en su sistema y que paguen impuestos adicionales.

Más detalles en www.mueveteconinteligencia.news

node.text:
TUDO FORA DO NORMAL ,QUE AGORA PASSA SER NORMAL 
.
.
.
.

Quantas mães não estão passando pelo desafio de, ensinar seus filhos a ter uma rotina de  atividades escolar em casa ??
.
.

Se esse “NOVO” método é bom ou não difícil dizer !
O difícil é pensar somente em nós,e nos nossos filhos.
👍🏻👎🏼👍🏻👎🏼👍🏻👎🏼👍🏻

Nem todas crianças tem  acesso a essa tecnologia, nem mesmo um celular quem dirá um Wifi.

💻🖱📡🖥

Como ficam essas crianças?? Sem estudar?
Será um ano perdido,sem ensino?

🤔🤔🤔🤔

Ou serão todos aprovados no final do ano,sem ter participado de nenhuma AULA ONLINE. 

😶😶😶😶😶

Muitas dessas crianças,tinha escola como sua segunda casa,professores viram (TIAS),o lanche já era o almoço.


Como tudo isso vai ficar ??

node.text:
Amway se asocia con la startup de microbiomas HEM para desarrollar suplementos probióticos personalizados

La empresa líder en salud y bienestar Amway anunció hoy una inversión estratégica y una asociación con Holzapfel Effective Microbes (HEM) con sede en Corea del Sur . Juntas, las empresas desarrollarán probióticos personalizados con el objetivo de apoyar el bienestar a través de beneficios relacionados con la salud intestinal , como inmunidad, control de peso, salud cerebral, salud de la piel y más.

node.text:
Uber saldrá de California por regulaciones del Estado!
California ( USA ), 22 de agosto (MCI) – A Uber se suma también Lyft, quienes tendrán que cerrar completamente las operaciones en California. Arruinan empresas y el empleo de miles de personas. Este viernes, Uber y Lyft cerraron completamente las operaciones de transporte compartido en California.

En septiembre de 2019, la legislatura del estado de California aprobó la AB 5, una ahora famosa ley que restringe severamente la contratación independiente y el trabajo por cuenta propia en muchas industrias. Al requerir que las aplicaciones de uso compartido como Uber y Lyft reclasifiquen a sus conductores como empleados de pleno derecho, la ley ordenó que las compañías provean asistencia médica y beneficios a todos los conductores en su sistema y que paguen impuestos adicionales.

Más detalles en www.mueveteconinteligencia.news

node.text:
Palitos de Pollo con Tocineta y Queso Azul😍
.
Ingredientes:

4 Milanesas de pollo
12 lonjas de Tocineta
150 ml de vino blanco
Aceite de oliva
Sal
Pimienta
Perejil

Salsa :

200 ml de nata líquida o crema de leche
150g de Queso Azul
1 cucharadita de maicena

Preparación:

Precalentar el horno a 200°C.

Cortar las milanesas en tiras de 3cm de ancho y salpimentar.

Enrollar las lonjas de tocineta alrededor de cada bastoncillo de pollo y fijarlas con un palillo de diente o hilo de cocina.

Dorar los bastoncillos envueltos en tocineta en una sartén con un poco de aceite y colocarlos en una bandeja de horno.

Añadimos el vino blanco y horneamos entre 10 y 15 minutos.

Para preparar la salsa colocar la nata (crema de leche) y el queso azul en una cacerola y calentar a fuego lento mezclando con una espátula.

A parte, disolver la maicena en una cuchara con agua fría e incorporarla a la salsa.

Mezclar y dejar a fuego lento 2 minutos más.

Servir acompañado de papas fritas y añadir un poco de perejil fresco en el último momento.
.

Posted @withregram • @khaledbeydoun Prison inmates are being “hired” to fight the #fires in #California.  This is concerning on a number of fronts, mainly:

— they’re being paid next to nothing 
— they’re not fully skilled or trained
— they’re risking their lives 
— full time firemen are at home because of #COVID
— the vast majority of these inmates are Black and Brown

Another bleak dimension of the prison industrial complex in the US.
